      "review_summary": "The PR propagates an optional `terminalError` from embedded attempts into run metadata and adds `non_deliverable_terminal_turn`-specific user-facing failure copy.\n\nPR surface: Source +26. Total +26 across 7 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main records `non_deliverable_terminal_turn` in attempt trajectory events and returns generic incomplete-turn metadata without a downstream specific reply path. I did not rerun the reporter's high-cache Telegram DM scenario live.",
